OL,6,FA rapist who is already serving a 20-
OL,7,Fyear jail term has been given another
OL,8,Fprison sentence of 18 years, after
OL,9,Fanother victim came forward to report
OL,10,Fher ordeal to police.
OL,12,FHarold Nicholson, 75, formerly of
OL,13,FHolywell Crescent, , is already behind
OL,14,Fbars after being found guilty in 2021
OL,15,Fof raping a young girl repeatedly in
OL,16,Fthe 1990s.
OL,18,FFollowing that conviction, another
OL,19,Fvictim reported being subjected to
OL,20,Fsexual abuse between the mid-1990s and
OL,21,Fmid-2000s.
